CAUTION -- PLEASE READ BEFORE PURCHASE
Game of Thrones Hero Boxes that have been opened can appear unopened on third party marketplaces. To ensure a Hero Box you wish to purchase is unopened, purchase directly at [Niftys.com/c/gameofthrones/marketplace](https://niftys.com/c/gameofthrones/marketplace).

Open this box at [Niftys.com](https://niftys.com/c/gameofthrones/campaign/unveil)

Nifty's, Daz3D, HBO, and Warner Bros. Discovery Global Consumer Products present Game of Thrones: Build Your Realm Hero Box.  The North, Series I.
